Name:                backup-rotate
Version:             0.1
Stability:           unstable
Description:         Simple rotation for hourly/daily/weekly or custom backups
Category:            System
Homepage:            http://github.com/JLimperg/backup-rotate
License:             MIT
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Jannis Limperg
Maintainer:          jannis@limperg.de
Build-Type:          Simple
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.16
x-follows-version-policy: Semantic Versioning

